The <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</a> <strong><code>align-items</code></strong> property sets the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-self" title="The align-self CSS property overrides a grid or flex item's align-items value. In Grid, it aligns the item inside theÂ grid area. In Flexbox, it aligns the item on the cross axis."><code>align-self</code></a> value on all direct children as a group.